Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.card

Class Face

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.card.Face
Direct Known Subclasses:
Back, Front
public abstract class Face extends Object
Immutable class representing the Face card. The face can be either the front or the back.

    • Face

      public Face(CardColor color, Map<CornerPosition,Corner> corners, CalculatePoints calculator) throws IllegalArgumentException
      Constructs a face card with the color and corners provided.
      Parameters:
      color - the face's color. If null, it represents a face without a color, for example a starting card.
      corners - contains corners to be inserted as card's corner.
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if cornerList has not 4 corners or any of them is null. or calculator is null.
